<l>allatu kiḷappiṉum vēṟṟumaik kaṇṇu</l>
<l>mellā viṟutiyu mukara nilaiyum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Both in non-case relationship and in case-relationship,</l>
<l>in all [the above-mentioned six kinds of words]</l>
<l>[the shortened] <foreign xml:lang="ta">u</foreign> stands finally.<note place="foot">E.g., <foreign xml:lang="ta">nāku kaṭitu, varaku kaṭitu</foreign> (both <foreign xml:lang="ta">allatu kiḷappiṉ,</foreign> in non-case relationship), <foreign xml:lang="ta">nāku kaṭumai, varaku kaṭumai</foreign> (both <foreign xml:lang="ta">
          vēṟṟumaikkaṇ,</foreign> in case-relationship).</note></l>
      </lg>
